
                    geant4-00-01-ref-06
                    ===================

geant4-00-01-ref-06 is geant4-00-01-ref-05 plus:

em-V00-01-01                 For next release (see below).
emlowen-V00-01-00            Bug fix to the above.
photolepton_hadron-00-01-00  Bug fix.
examples-V00-01-09           Changes to .out files for the above.

------------------------------------------------------
em-V00-01-01:

electromagnetic/standard:
    muls: Fine tuning and bug fixed for low energy e-.
          Inclusion of nuclear size effect for high energy
           (e > 100 Mev, h > 1 GeV)

    IonisationPlus: production version for electrons and hadrons.

    Eloss fluctuation: use G4Poisson instead of CLHEP.

    PAI model: bugs fixed

electromagnetic/lowEnergy:
   hadron ionisation implemented.
   ion    ionisation implemented.
   minor bug fixed in photo electric. 

electromagnetic/xrays:
   bug fixed in cerenkov.

electromagnetic/test:
  TestEm6 for low energy hadron.
  All tests moved in examples/extended/electromagnetic.
